This line still is not correct. The way SLF4J works, is it substitutes the {} for each parameter in turn. If the last parameter is a Throwable, it prints the stack trace after the log message. So I think it should be:
LOG.debug("Pipeline not found in pipeline state manager during" +
            " pipeline creation. PipelineID: {}", pid, e);

